 444:src/main.c    ****    * Immediately clear MOE on both motor timers to force hi-Z (free-wheel):
 445:src/main.c    ****    *   MOE=0 + OSSR=0 + OSSI=0 → all timer outputs disabled → phases float.
 446:src/main.c    ****    * Without this, setup.c leaves MOE=1 with CCR=0 → complementary PWM drives
 447:src/main.c    ****    * all low-side gates HIGH → all motor phases shorted to GND → wheel locked.
